  "description": "A lightweight curated Claude Code skillset for .NET developers. Combines a customized fork of obra/superpowers (workflow), a trimmed fork of Aaronontheweb/dotnet-skills (patterns + agents), and adapted skills from mattpocock/skills (grill-me, design-an-interface). Tuned for .NET 10 + Aspire + Minimal API + NHibernate or EF Core projects with Vue or Blazor frontends. Key overrides: AskUserQuestion-first brainstorming (with deferred-tool preload), domain-first planning before TDD, and executing-plans preferred over subagent-driven-development.",
